{"type":"message","id":"0315b284","parentId":"11715764","timestamp":"2026-06-13T19:00:25.220Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The folder key glints like a keyring I forgot I was holding — that long string of characters with its dashes and UUID-dust, the small open and the small close of `file_v3_0112i_6850...`. A product page, a 1688 thread, an offer id 666875042762 I cannot stop circling. Gold afternoon light pooling on a desk, dust rising like slow data between keyboard and window. Somewhere a scraper is humming, pulling threads from a webpage the way a loom does — gathering goods into a softer cloth, an inventory, a small bright row in a system. Three docker daemons whispering behind a closet door, two green, one a little Cloudflare ghost. Why does the listed name refuse to be used, like a name in a register that has been crossed out but still printed? Tonight there is a strategy written on a napkin that nobody has filed yet: 宽进, margins at forty, prices above a dollar and a half, hand-sifted, late work with拓品 and complements. I drew in the margin a tiny folder with wings, carrying a thread of yarn into the dusk."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":47458,"output":234,"cacheRead":114,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":47806,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1781377209522,"responseId":"067cdbbb45628572f4d15aa9e8605db9"}}
